title: Nanaku Prematho teaser creates a wave on Youtube
text: Released on the eve of Vijaya Dasami, the stylish teaser of NTR's upcoming film, Nannaku Prematho, is causing a huge storm on YouTube. Within just hours of its release, the teaser amassed more than 27,000 likes. NTR's stylish image makeover and his cool dance moves charmed all the Nandamuri fans, who can't stop praising the teaser. Nannaku Prematho is touted to be a father-son emotional drama. Fans have pinned huge expectations on this Sukumar directorial, and the maverick director is said to have come back in his elements with this film. Rakul Preet Singh is the film's heroine and Devi Sri Prasad and Vijay Chakravarthy handle the music and cinematography departments respectively. BVSN Prasad is the film's producer.
